All he knows is Geppetto.

39:48.261 --> 39:49.763
Yeah, but...

39:49.930 --> 39:51.598
He's not gonna say anything
about you, Kelly.

39:51.765 --> 39:53.558
I mean, the guy's
head over heels.

39:53.725 --> 39:56.395
And I know that makes you feel guilty,
and I feel guilty too.

39:56.561 --> 39:58.647
David's drowning,
and if we're not careful,

39:58.814 --> 40:00.524
he's gonna pull us under
with him.

40:00.690 --> 40:03.068
It's like the three of us
were on a yacht, OK,

40:03.235 --> 40:06.571
