circle back and get him.

40:18.917 --> 40:20.627
You know, like in 15 years,

40:20.794 --> 40:23.713
whatever the federal mandatory
sentencing guidelines are

40:23.880 --> 40:25.340
for bank robbery.

40:25.507 --> 40:27.467
And by the way,
we're talking about federal prison.

40:27.634 --> 40:29.136
