43:40.869 --> 43:42.996
Just one little thing, baby,
to celebrate.

43:43.163 --> 43:45.081
And maybe just a little,
you know,

43:45.248 --> 43:46.875
like, a little something
for the boys.

43:47.042 --> 43:48.835
No, no. Now, Michelle, please,
don't push it.

43:49.002 --> 43:50.879
I'm not gonna do anything
for the kids.

43:51.046 --> 43:53.131
They gotta learn that presents

43:53.298 --> 43:55.425
