Dammit!

46:14.606 --> 46:16.357
Oh, what do I do?
What do I say?

46:16.524 --> 46:19.402
Pick it up, but if it's him,
find out where he is.

46:19.569 --> 46:22.405
OK, but this time
get the room number.

46:23.448 --> 46:24.908
- Hello?
- DAVID: Hey, Kelly?

46:25.074 --> 46:26.868
