- Had to make myself a disguise.

46:35.418 --> 46:37.796
I look like Gene Shalit
from 'The Today Show'.

46:37.962 --> 46:39.589
(WHISPERS) Location -
find out where he is.

46:39.756 --> 46:41.341
You tell me
how it's going down here.

46:41.508 --> 46:44.135
So, um, where are you exactly?

46:44.302 --> 46:47.388
Cozumel. It's an island
right off the coast a ways.

46:47.555 --> 46:49.265
