his exact location,

49:11.074 --> 49:13.284
so you're gonna have to do
a little bit of intel.

49:13.451 --> 49:15.620
Mm-hm. I don't mind the hunt.

49:15.787 --> 49:17.413
I bet you don't.

49:17.580 --> 49:19.374
