49:43.147 --> 49:46.192
Something to choke him.

49:46.359 --> 49:48.528
'Cause I like the struggle.

49:49.696 --> 49:51.656
I prefer it.

49:51.823 --> 49:54.242
'Cause when I take a life,
I like to take it.

49:54.409 --> 49:56.411
It ain't your life no more.

49:56.577 --> 49:58.413
It's my life.

