50:24.731 --> 50:26.733
And I'm not about to have
my pocket picked.

50:26.899 --> 50:28.818
No, no, siree Bob!

50:28.985 --> 50:30.570
Especially by this cat
right here.

50:30.737 --> 50:32.447
Look at him. Look at him.

50:32.613 --> 50:35.450
He look like Kenny Rogers
