on the inside.

50:43.833 --> 50:47.462
Yeah, and you know what, bruh?
You'd better start talking.

50:47.628 --> 50:49.505
If we don't find out
who stole that money,

50:49.672 --> 50:51.340
we gonna lock somebody up.

50:51.507 --> 50:54.177
You know who that is?
This dude right here.

50:54.343 --> 50:56.387
Yep. It's a nice picture,
