- Nobody.

51:06.939 --> 51:09.108
Who was he close to, man?
I know you know!

51:09.275 --> 51:11.277
Wait, wait. There was a girl.
There was a girl.

51:11.444 --> 51:13.946
There was a girl,
she quit about a month ago.

51:14.113 --> 51:15.698
About a month ago.
Is that right?

51:15.865 --> 51:17.658
- Had a real white girl name.
- White girl name.

51:17.825 --> 51:20.036
