51:31.422 --> 51:33.132
I don't damn know.

51:33.299 --> 51:35.760
Katie Candy Cane,
I'm coming for you, baby.

51:35.927 --> 51:38.763
Yep, you and all
your stripper friends.

51:38.930 --> 51:42.517
I was wondering if you had
an American man staying there.

51:42.683 --> 51:44.477
He... Um...
How would I describe him?

51:44.644 --> 51:47.146
He's, um, got a lot
of body hair.

51:47.313 --> 51:49.023
He's kinda short.

51:49.190 --> 51:51.526
Um, looks like
one of the 12 apostles.

51:51.692 --> 51:53.486
You have three men
that are staying there

51:53.653 --> 51:56.239
that fit that description?

51:56.405 --> 51:59.659
OK, well, can I please leave
