01:03:47.574 --> 01:03:49.117
MAN: They even led us
to believe

01:03:49.284 --> 01:03:51.203
that David Ghantt may have
held a torch for you.

01:03:51.370 --> 01:03:54.164
- Huh?
- That he was in love with you.

01:03:56.041 --> 01:03:57.417
(LAUGHS)

01:03:57.584 --> 01:03:59.878
That's crazy.

01:04:00.045 --> 01:04:02.047
Please.

01:04:02.214 --> 01:04:04.383
Miss Kelly, you...you alright?

01:04:04.550 --> 01:04:08.262
Yeah. I just have, um,
some seasonal allergies.

01:04:08.428 --> 01:04:11.348
Think I'm allergic
to those flowers or something.

01:04:12.391 --> 01:04:13.767
(LAUGHS)

01:04:13.934 --> 01:04:16.228
- Plastic flowers?
- Yeah.

01:04:16.395 --> 01:04:20.065
It's the craziest thing.
Will you excuse me for a minute?

01:04:21.400 --> 01:04:23.652
She called me a dude.

01:04:23.819 --> 01:04:27.072
(SOBS)

01:04:35.497 --> 01:04:37.291
(PHONE RINGS)

01:04:37.457 --> 01:04:40.127
Damn it! Can...
Can somebody get the...

01:04:44.423 --> 01:04:47.134
- Hello?
- Yeah. This Steve Chambers?

01:04:47.301 --> 01:04:51.638
- H-how'd you get this number?
- Mike McKinney had it on him.

01:04:51.805 --> 01:04:53.515
Where's Mike McKinney?

01:04:53.682 --> 01:04:55.392
That ain't
none of your business.

01:04:55.559 --> 01:04:58.937
- OK, D-David, take it easy.
- No, you take it easy.

01:04:59.104 --> 01:05:02.065
I opened a Mexican bank account
and here's what I expect.

01:05:02.232 --> 01:05:04.526
Now, wait a second, Ghantt!
Hold it!

01:05:04.693 --> 01:05:08.447
I expect $6 million down there
two days from this very second.

01:05:08.614 --> 01:05:11.366
I'm starting to feel like
a corn dog at a hot dog party,

01:05:11.533 --> 01:05:13.201
and it ain't flattering,
I'll tell you that!

01:05:13.368 --> 01:05:15.078
And I'm starting
to lose my temper.

01:05:15.245 --> 01:05:17.164
David, I-I don't know
what you think is happening,

01:05:17.331 --> 01:05:19.374
but I am not your enemy, OK?

01:05:19.541 --> 01:05:21.043
Listen to me.

01:05:21.209 --> 01:05:22.711
The name of the bank
is Banco Lujo.

01:05:22.878 --> 01:05:25.589
If there ain't
$6 million in there

01:05:25.756 --> 01:05:28.342
two days from this very minute,

01:05:28.508 --> 01:05:31.511
I will turn myself in
to the interpolice

01:05:31.678 --> 01:05:34.056
and yours will be
the first name I give 'em.

01:05:34.222 --> 01:05:35.641
(HANGS UP)

01:05:35.807 --> 01:05:38.852
Ghantt! Sonofa... God!

